xserver-xorg-video-imx (2.0.1-201100909) maverick; urgency=low

  * release version (match imx-graphics version)
  * PictOpAdd, PictOpIn blending modes
  * Xv double buffering refinements (fullscreen videos will double buffer to reduce tearing)
  * Xv no longer draws over windows while using a compositing window manager
  * EXA optimizations, reduce redundant code and improve memory allocation to be less aggressive

 -- Martin Krastev <martin.krastev@genesi-usa.com>  Fri, 09 Sep 2011 13:53:33 -0600

